Package: surVisualiser
Type: Package
Title: Multi-Dimensional Survival Analysis and Visualization for TCGA Transcriptome Data
Version: 0.99.1
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Yuhan",
    family = "Sun",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "yzsun0123@gmail.com",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-3510-5964"))
Description: Provides a streamlined workflow for analyzing TCGA transcriptome
    data. Includes functions for reading and aggregating transcript-level
    expression, integrating clinical survival metadata, performing immune cell
    deconvolution via CIBERSORT, generating Kaplan-Meier survival plots with
    flexible grouping strategies, per-sample pre-ranked GSEA against MSigDB
    hallmarks with circular-analysis-safe secretome gene exclusion, and
    side-by-side Tumor / Normal / difference heatmaps of hallmark-secretome
    correlations. Designed for reproducible cancer genomics research.
